---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | CM Web Solutions">
    <Header transparent={false} />

    <main class="page-content">
        <div class="container page-container">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to home</a>

            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

            <section>
                <h2>Who we are</h2>
                <p>CM Web Solutions provides website subscription services for UK businesses. We are a sole trader based in the United Kingdom. If you have any questions about this policy, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@cmwebsolutions.com">hello@cmwebsolutions.com</a>.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>What data we collect and why</h2>

                <h3>Plausible Analytics (anonymous usage data)</h3>
                <p>We use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong> to understand how visitors use our website. Plausible is privacy-first, cookie-free, and does not collect any personal data. No cookies are set, and no personally identifiable information (PII) is tracked. The data collected includes anonymous page views, referral sources, browsers, and device types. This helps us improve the website without compromising your privacy.</p>

                <h3>Contact form data</h3>
                <p>When you submit our consultation form, we collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your name</li>
                    <li>Your email address</li>
                    <li>Your phone number (optional)</li>
                    <li>Your business type (optional)</li>
                    <li>Your message</li>
                </ul>
                <p>This information is used solely to respond to your enquiry. We will only contact you about the matter you raise. We do not use this data for marketing purposes without your explicit consent.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>How we store your data</h2>
                <p>Contact form submissions are stored securely and are only accessible to the business owner. We take reasonable steps to protect your personal data against loss, misuse, and unauthorised access.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Data retention</h2>
                <p>We retain contact form data for as long as necessary to deal with your enquiry, and for up to 12 months afterwards. You may request deletion at any time.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Third-party services</h2>
                <p>We use the following third-party services that may process data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Plausible Analytics</strong> — anonymous website analytics (no personal data collected)</li>
                    <li><strong>Astro / Netlify</strong> — website hosting and deployment</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal data to third parties.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Your rights under UK GDPR</h2>
                <p>Under UK data protection law, you have the following rights:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The right to be informed about how we use your data</li>
                    <li>The right to access the personal data we hold about you</li>
                    <li>The right to request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                    <li>The right to request deletion of your data</li>
                    <li>The right to restrict processing of your data</li>
                    <li>The right to data portability</li>
                </ul>
                <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@cmwebsolutions.com">hello@cmwebsolutions.com</a>.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
            </section>

            <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to home</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-content {
        padding-top: 120px;
        padding-bottom: 92px;
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .page-container {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .back-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        transition: opacity 180ms ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
        opacity: 0.7;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .updated {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    section h2 {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    section h3 {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        margin-top: 24px;
    }

    section p {
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    section ul {
        margin: 12px 0;
        padding-left: 24px;
    }

    section li {
        color: var(--muted-strong);
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    section a {
        color: var(--primary);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .page-content :global(.container) {
        width: min(100% - 40px, 760px);
    }
</style>
